  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or Stuttgart approach charts 11-1, 11-1A, 11-2, 11-2A from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.<br>An aircraft departed from Stuttgart airport on Runway 25, but due to a passenger's serious illness, the pilot decided to turn back and land at Stuttgart airport following the ILS CAT I Rwy 25 approach procedure. Which approach chart should the pilot use ?</p>",
